    "slug": "extend-rf-boundaries-harogic-launches-new-sga-60-usb-vector-signal-genetor",
    "title": "Extend RF Boundaries: HAROGIC Launches New SGA-60 USB Vector Signal Genetor",
    "date": "04 / 23 2026",
    "excerpt": "HAROGIC Launches New SGA-60 Vector Signal Generator",
    "cover_img": "https://www.harogic.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/SOP-SGA_中文官网新闻内页小图708x394-副本.jpg",
    "content": "<div class=\"detail-description hyphenate\"><article class=\"4ever-article\">\n<h6><a href=\"https://www.harogic.cn/product/sga-60-vector-signal-generator/\"><span data-type=\"text\">This next-generation USB-powered Vector Signal Generator (VSG) is engineered to bridge the gap between laboratory-grade precision and the portability required for modern field operations, RD and T&amp;M. By offering a combination of low phase noise and expansive modulation capabilities, the SGA-60 provides a formidable alternative to traditional signal generators, setting a new benchmark for performance-to-size ratio in the sub-6 GHz market.</span></a></h6>\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"size-full wp-image-16618 aligncenter\" height=\"900\" src=\"https://www.harogic.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/HAROGIC-PXN90-SPECTRUM-ANALYZER-AND-SGA60.png\" style=\"width: 60%; height: auto; display: block; margin: 24px auto;\" width=\"1536\">\n<h6>The SGA-60 series represents a significant advancement in high-performance vector signal generation, engineered to provide a seamless balance between laboratory-grade precision and commercial accessibility. Covering an expansive frequency range from 9 kHz to 6 GHz, the SGA-60 is designed to meet the rigorous demands of modern wireless communication, aerospace, and education sectors. It offers a robust 100 MHz instantaneous bandwidth for complex wideband signal generation, complemented by 50 MHz of real-time streaming bandwidth, ensuring high-fidelity signal playback and continuous data throughput for sophisticated simulation environments.</h6>\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"size-full wp-image-16613 aligncenter\" height=\"800\" src=\"https://www.harogic.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/HAROGIC-AM.png\" style=\"width: 50%; height: auto; display: block; margin: 24px auto;\" width=\"1280\">\n<h6>Beyond its core specifications, the SGA-60 series is a versatile powerhouse capable of generating a diverse array of signal types. From standard Continuous Wave (CW) and traditional analog modulations (AM/FM) to advanced digitally modulated signals, the series provides engineers with a comprehensive toolkit for every stage of development. The inclusion of high-speed frequency and amplitude sweeps, as well as chirp signal generation, makes it particularly effective for radar testing and component characterization. By delivering these high-end capabilities at an affordable price point, the SGA-60 series democratizes precision RF testing, allowing labs and production facilities to scale their capabilities without the prohibitive costs usually associated with 6 GHz vector signal generators.</h6>\n<h6>The hardware design focuses on flexibility and durability without compromising the intrument’s compact footprint. With a typicla output amplitude range of -100 dBm to +10 dBm, the SGA-60 can simulate everything from the weak signals found at a receiver’s edge to the robust signals required for amplifier characterization. Its USB-powered architecture allows for seamless integration into existing software-defined environments, offering a streamlined workflow that reduces setup time and equipment overhead. Whether deployed in a high-density lab environment or used for system integration, SGA-60 provides the stability and repeatability that professionals demand.</h6>\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"size-full wp-image-16614 aligncenter\" height=\"798\" src=\"https://www.harogic.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/64QAM-英.png\" style=\"width: 50%; height: auto; display: block; margin: 24px auto;\" width=\"1276\">\n<h5>About HAROGIC</h5>\n<h6>Headquartered in Singapore, HAROGIC is a premier developer of software-defined radio frequency test and measurement instrumentation. HAROGIC is dedicated to providing the compact, robust, high-performance RF hardware with agile, intelligent software to help our customers extend RF boundaries.</h6>\n</img></img></img></article></div>",
    "permalink": "https://www.harogic.com/latest-news/extend-rf-boundaries-harogic-launches-new-sga-60-usb-vector-signal-genetor/"
